If you're craving breakfast food, lunch food, dinner food, or any sort of dessert, then GL has your desire at your fingertips. If you order it for delivery, it is always at your door in thirty minutes at the most. My personal favorites: -egg white and spinach omelette-- always perfect and still warm and delicious. -veggie gyro: peeeerfect pita and I love the yogurt tahini and yummy vegetables that are always perfectly ripe. -Falafel is amaaaaazing The staff is super incredible and the prices are fair. I don't know why there isn't always an incredibly long line, but I'm not sure I mind :P Check it out.
